%define        gemname ucf

Name:          gem-ucf
Version:       2.0.2
Release:       alt1
Summary:       This is a Ruby library for working with UCF documents
License:       BSD
Group:         Development/Ruby
Url:           http://mygrid.github.io/ruby-ucf/
